<section id="about" class="about">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="about-content">
			<div class="about-text">
				<h2 class="section-title">About Dillz Bites</h2>
				<p>Welcome to Dillz Bites, where every cake is a masterpiece and every bite tells a story. Our passion for baking began with a simple dream: to create beautiful, delicious cakes that bring joy to life's most special moments.</p>
				<p>Using only the finest ingredients and time-honored techniques, we craft each cake with meticulous attention to detail. From elegant wedding cakes to whimsical birthday celebrations, we specialize in custom designs that perfectly capture your vision.</p>
				<div class="features">
					<div class="feature">
						<h3>‚ú® Custom Designs</h3>
						<p>Every cake is uniquely crafted to your specifications</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature">
						<h3>üéÇ Premium Ingredients</h3>
						<p>We use only the finest, freshest ingredients</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature">
						<h3>üíù Made with Love</h3>
						<p>Each creation is handcrafted with passion and care</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		padding: 80px 0;
		background: var(--light-purple);
	}

	.section-title {
		font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
		font-size: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		background: var(--gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.about-content {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.about-text p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--black);
	}

	.features {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}

	.feature {
		background: white;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 15px;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.feature:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.feature h3 {
		color: var(--primary-pink);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}

	/* Mobile Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.features {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
	}
</style> 